<plot>Tom is an ordinary guy struggling to come to terms with a recent difficult breakup. Sympathizing with his plight, and as way for them to have some fun, friends Jay and Kevin arrange a special evening to help him get his mind off of his ex. But Jay makes a slight mistake landing them in an unexpected encounter with Anton, a disgruntled French host. The situation soon deteriorates as all three find themselves at a loss for words in this comedy gone wrong in a midtown Manhattan bar.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423587</url></doc>
